description: Erection of new housing comprising of 155 residential units (24x1 bedroom flats, 80x2 bedroom flats, 32x3 bedroom flats, 8x4 bedroom flats and 11x5 bedroom dwellings) in four blocks varying from 3 to 5 storeys, with new access road, 54 car parking spaces, amenity space and the demolition of existing housing estate.
